message: Dear Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which holds significant value to us and is tailored to meet your specific needs. Given its importance to both parties, we propose a transaction price of $11,000. This figure reflects a fair compromise between its intrinsic value and your perceived worth, aiming to ensure mutual satisfaction. We believe this offer presents an excellent opportunity for you to acquire a valuable asset at a competitive rate. Please let us know if you require any further information or clarification, or if you're ready to proceed with this proposal.
